*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZGAMZEY_EASY_RB_CB
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zgy_easy_rb_cb.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK b WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-001.
PARAMETERS:
  p_num1 TYPE i,
  p_num2 TYPE i.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK b.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK a WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-000.
PARAMETERS:
  rb1 RADIOBUTTON GROUP a,
  rb2 RADIOBUTTON GROUP a,
  rb3 RADIOBUTTON GROUP a,
  rb4 RADIOBUTTON GROUP a,
  cb1 AS CHECKBOX,
  cb2 AS CHECKBOX.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK a.

DATA:gv_result TYPE i.

IF rb1 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM addition.
ELSEIF rb2 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM substraction.
ELSEIF rb3 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM multiplication.
ELSEIF rb4 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM division.
ENDIF.

IF cb1 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM on_ile_carp.
ENDIF.

IF cb2 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM ikiye_bol.
ENDIF.

WRITE:gv_result.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form ADDITION
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM addition .
gv_result = p_num1 + p_num2.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form SUBSTRACTION
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM substraction .
gv_result = p_num1 - p_num2.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form MULTIPLICATION
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM multiplication .
gv_result = p_num1 * p_num2.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form DIVISION
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM division .
gv_result = p_num1 / p_num2.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form ON_ILE_CARP
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM on_ile_carp .
gv_result = gv_result * 10.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form IKIYE_BOL
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM ikiye_bol .
gv_result = gv_result / 2.
ENDFORM.
